Phobias computers show an incredible amount of eneggy built up.

"What's this?" Phobia asked himself, unsure what to make of the 
anomaly. His ship had recorded multiple anomalies since his arrival 
but this was the biggest one yet, even bigger then the anomalie from 
the Iron fists destruction of the mountain.

(Is the gateway from past cybertron or future cybertron? if it's the 
past then Unicron wouldn't have been destroyed yet so he wouldn't be 
back, he'd just exist.)
